title: The Joe Rogan Experience Review of the week
description:
Episodes 1135 - 1138

 

What an incredible week of guests.  Such amazing episodes and for 30 minutes I delve into it. 

 

Guests included:

Ari Shaffir - comedian, world class shit talker. 

Hamilton Morris - TV show host and psychedelic adventurer.

Duncan Trussell - comedian,  sweetheart of a guy. 

Ted Nugent - Rockstar, avid hunter and gun owner

 

Enjoy folks!
